  Heidi wowed in an asymmetric, baby pink slip dress with one side coming all the way up to the top of her thigh. The garment featured white lace detailing and she accessorised with a lacey teal cardigan and black string necklace. Next, the star could be seen flipping her long hair in a glamorous beach clip, which saw her posing on her knees in the sand. Heidi donned a patterned, multi-coloured bikini with a high waist and wore the straps loosely around her arms.  